@no_majority
title: There is no clear governing majority.
view-if: vf_seats_upper_austria <= 25 and oclk_seats_upper_austria <= 25

The incumbent administration continues to govern as a minority government.



@vf_majority
title: The <span style="color: #ED2939;">**VF**</span> forms a majority government.
subtitle: <span style="color: #ED2939;">**VF**</span> ([+ vf_ul +]%)
view-if: vf_seats_upper_austria > 25
on-arrival: {!
Q.upper_austria_oclk = 0;
Q.upper_austria_vf = 1;

Q.in_vf_majority_upper_austria = 1;
Q.in_oclk_majority_upper_austria = 0;
!}

